sequenceDiagram
  participant A as Client A
  participant W as WebSocket server
  participant P as PostgreSQL
  participant R as Redis
  participant O as Room + OT
  participant B as Client B

  A->>W: authenticate(token)
  W->>P: verify active user
  A->>W: join_document(documentId)
  W->>P: load document and permission
  W->>R: GETEX active state
  W->>O: create/join room
  W-->>A: document_joined(content, revision, role)
  W-->>B: presence(count)

  A->>W: edit(baseRevision, operationId, splice)
  W->>O: transform, apply, increment
  W-->>A: edit_accepted(transformed splice, revision)
  W->>R: SET full state with TTL
  W-->>B: edit(transformed splice, revision, user)
  W->>P: debounced revision-aware state write
